<p><b>Windows Vista</b>, an <a href="/wiki/Operating_system" title="Operating system">operating system</a> released by <a href="/wiki/Microsoft" title="Microsoft">Microsoft</a> in November 2006, has received substantial criticism by reviewers and users. Due to issues with privacy, security, performance, and <a href="/wiki/Product_activation" title="Product activation">product activation</a>, <a href="/wiki/Windows_Vista" title="Windows Vista">Windows Vista</a> has been the subject of a number of negative assessments by various groups.</p>
