<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://h10025.www1.hp.com/ewfrf/wc/document?lc=en&amp;cc=us&amp;docname=c00678204&amp;dlc=en" class="external text" title="http://h10025.www1.hp.com/ewfrf/wc/document?lc=en&amp;cc=us&amp;docname=c00678204&amp;dlc=en" rel="nofollow">in here, HP states that it wont release vista drivers for some hardware. Together with the fact that the old drivers can't be loaded, this renders such hardware unusable under vista</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.linchpinlabs.com/resources/atsiv/usage-design.html" class="external text" title="http://www.linchpinlabs.com/resources/atsiv/usage-design.html" rel="nofollow">Linchpin Labs Response to Microsoft's Classification of Atsiv</a></li>
